cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on the control of a multi-rotor micro-aerial vehicle (MAV) and the use of a model predictive controller (MPC) to improve its performance. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper describes the identification of the dynamics of the vehicle and autopilot controllers, which is a key aspect of control systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The use of a model predictive controller (MPC) involves machine learning techniques to predict the future behavior of the system and optimize the control inputs. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of machine learning techniques in the design of the MPC falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not the main focus of the paper, the use of a motion capture system to evaluate the control performance involves computer vision techniques.
